<h2 id="一、clear-函数方法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#一、clear-函数方法" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 一、clear() 函数方法</h2>
<p>  clear()函数是一个非常有用的函数，能够快速、简单地清空列表和字典的所有元素。通过使用clear()函数，我们可以重复利用列表对象、清空缓存数据等，提高代码的性能和效率。<br>
  但需要注意，在使用clear()函数时要谨慎操作。</p>
<p>  此方法仅支持可变容器类型，比如：列表、字节数组、字典和集合。语法如下：</p>
<div class="language-python line-numbers-mode" data-ext="py"><pre v-pre class="language-python"><code>a<span class="token punctuation">.</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>           <span class="token comment"># 通用语法</span>
<span class="token builtin">list</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># 列表</span>
<span class="token builtin">bytearray</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>   <span class="token comment"># 字节数组</span>
<span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># 字典</span>
<span class="token builtin">set</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>         <span class="token comment"># 集合</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul>
<li>【示例1】</li>
</ul>
